---
title: Herby Seared Salmon & Veggie Fries with Onion Chutney Sauce & Radish Salad
description: A delicious salmon can win over many hearts, and we believe this herby garlic version will make yours flutter. If that’s not enough though, maybe try one of the veggie fries. To really seal the deal, top the salmon with a sweet onion chutney sauce. Yum!

